_header: Naked into this world born am I
_description: ‘Of þe seuen ages’: a dialogue between man, the good angel, and the fiend — 56 lines in couplets and quatrains (abab)

BLAdd37049.First Lines:
Nakyd in to þis warlde I am norne am IAngel Loke
                    cristes commawndements þu kepe forþi…
BLAdd37049.Last Lines:
…And els in helle he hade had a placeEmange fyre & fendes
                    of vgly chere
